{"tid":957554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"火辣看護兼賣「原味內褲」年賺2百萬　只為救救流浪貓！","createTime":"2018-12-27T06:29:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T10:29:06.000Z","uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"27078545feb905b2702dc59df680b54c291c347c","tid":957554,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T06:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3792/3792936.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3792%2F3792936.jpg&h=0d652bac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲英國看護賣原味內褲救流浪貓。（圖／翻攝自Facebook／Raven Nix，下同）<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n英國看護妮可絲（Raven Nix）白天照顧病人，晚上還有份收入更高的副業，就是在網路上販售「原味內衣褲」。她表示，這還不是自己賣過最特別的東西，有不少客人甚至會出高價跟她買尿，平均一星期可以賣出1小罐40英鎊（約新台幣1600元）的尿，算是穩定銷量的商品。<br />\n據英國《都市日報》報導，妮可絲起初賣的是250英鎊（約新台幣1萬元）的原味拖鞋、3雙40英鎊（約新台幣1600元）的原味襪子，後來才慢慢增加了新品項「原味內衣褲」，也成為賣場裡最夯的搶手貨。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3792/3792935.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3792%2F3792935.jpg&h=83ea2c4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲她聲稱，有固定會回購的死忠粉絲。<br />\n她表示，靠販賣原味系列商品一年可賺6萬英鎊（約新台幣240萬元），但這些錢其實不是用來享樂，而是花費在貓咪身上。妮可絲說，自己是個重度貓奴，做這行是為了要賺錢來救流浪貓，原本有定期拍攝性感照來增加收入，大約5年前就有粉絲私訊她想買「原味內褲」，她才意識到這的確是個市場。<br />\n妮可絲強調，自己賺這些原味錢是想幫流浪貓建立遮風避雨的家，雖然一開始有點抗拒，但是「看到需要幫助的毛孩，我很難坐視不管。」而且男友也非常支持她經營這副業，甚至自己也有興趣加入這項行業。<br />\n▼妮可絲看護薪水用來付房租，賣原味商品的收入則拿來養貓。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3792/3792937.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3792%2F3792937.jpg&h=c1cf2b32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181227/1341647.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181227%2F1341647.htm&d=KPiejKE5eLK68LjQx65YEP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=a5b97179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181227/1341647.htm</a>"},{"pid":"eb4adba1f2c1e307a8596b3078a84116ce21da4e","tid":957554,"uid":21423,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T06:32:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ae39fde765003c87d4bbb3776072e35ba0524e7","tid":957554,"uid":194370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T06:33:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c3411620d8a3ed60d605116a6e77eeb0a8f9ee","tid":957554,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T06:34:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f212bc403a9e83c49e85f2d27848df6e544ffcca","tid":957554,"uid":10635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T06:34:49.000Z","msg":"送都唔要啦 屌。。。"},{"pid":"c3968c9366ece85a04109c0bd8219da9730c86d3","tid":957554,"uid":34189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T06:35:04.000Z","msg":"男友也非常支持她經營這副業，甚至自己也有興趣加入這項行業。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb401c8c82a1d51fa28e7424feaa45b70b6b012","tid":957554,"uid":8171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T06:35:24.000Z","msg":"村長個女...李愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df4ec8d771b190e8eedccd2c380aff1aec4b374","tid":957554,"uid":10056,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"c3968c9366ece85a04109c0bd8219da9730c86d3","tid":957554,"uid":34189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T06:35:04.000Z","msg":"男友也非常支持她經營這副業，甚至自己也有興趣加入這項行業。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T06:35:43.000Z","msg":"根本果d底褲就係佢男朋友既<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ebc2b634aeb68397496180a9808c94f2c66e94","tid":957554,"uid":60150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c